            <h2>FAQs</h2>
            <h3>How can I contact KLM Customer Service? </h3>
            <p>You can reach KLM customer service via phone numbers listed on your e-ticket, live chat on the KLM website, WhatsApp, Messenger, social media platforms like X (Twitter) and Facebook, or through email. </p>
            <h3>Can I manage my flight bookings online with KLM? </h3>
            <p>Yes, you can manage your bookings online through the KLM website or app. Options include changing flights, requesting refunds, checking baggage policies, adding extra services, and tracking flight status. </p>
            <h3>How do I file a complaint with KLM? </h3>
            <p>You can file a complaint using KLM’s online feedback form, which is available on their website. Once submitted, you'll receive a reference number to track the progress of your case. </p>
            <h3>Does KLM provide special assistance for passengers with disabilities? </h3>
